title: New Aliso Viejo eatery already giving back to community (City of Aliso Viejo, CA)
text: ( Source : City of Aliso Viejo, CA ) Jimboy's Tacos recently opened its first Orange County restaurant in Aliso Viejo . The quick-service taco eatery, known for its grilled Parmesan-crusted shell, is nestled in the former Jack in the Box site
